@startuml sequence_summary
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Relationship Summary

actor User
participant "ContactDetailPage" as UI
participant "GET /api/contacts/{id}/summary" as API
participant "AppDbContext" as CTX
queue "SummaryQueue" as Q
participant "SummaryWorker" as W
participant "IChatClient" as CC

User -> UI: open detail
UI -> API: GET summary
API -> CTX: SELECT summary
alt cached < 1h
    CTX --> API: row
    API --> UI: 200 { paragraph, stats, stale:false }
else stale / missing
    API -> Q: enqueue SummaryRefreshJob
    API --> UI: 200 existing (or 204)
    UI -> UI: poll every 1.5s (max 15s)
    W -> Q: ReadAllAsync
    W -> CTX: load contact + last 20 interactions
    W -> CC: CompleteAsync(system,user)
    CC --> W: {paragraph, sentiment}
    W -> CTX: UPSERT summary
    UI -> API: GET summary (poll)
    API -> CTX: SELECT
    CTX --> API: fresh row
    API --> UI: 200 fresh
end

User -> UI: tap Refresh
UI -> API: POST /api/.../summary:refresh
API --> UI: 202 (or 429)

@enduml
